_:N203310c447f8427ea3924e8b38bc38eb <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In the first place, contact us to set out your complaint and we will let you know the action we can take, or explain why we can’t take action.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_2258\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Enquiries</p>\n\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:clientdevelopment@voa.gov.uk\">clientdevelopment@voa.gov.uk</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<p>If you are not satisfied with our response and wish to make a formal complaint, follow the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/valuation-office-agency/about/complaints-procedure\" class=\"govuk-link\">Valuation Office Agency’s procedure</a>.</p>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
